---
description: 
globs: *.html
alwaysApply: false
---

Tables / Lists:
[dataId]="'users-table'"

Table Header:
[dataId]="'users-table-header'"

Table Rows:
[dataId]="'users-table-row'"

Table Columns:
[dataId]="'email-col'", [dataId]="'name-col'"

Form Elements:
[dataId]="'profile-form'"

Input Controls:
[dataId]="'email-input'", [dataId]="'phone-input'"

Action Buttons:
[dataId]="'submit-button'", [dataId]="'cancel-button'"

Modal/Dialog Elements:
[dataId]="'confirm-delete-modal'"

Modal Action Buttons:
[dataId]="'confirm-action-button'"

Tab Elements:
[dataId]="'settings-tab'", [dataId]="'notifications-tab'"

Loading Indicators:
[dataId]="'data-list-loader'"

Nested Component IDs: assign dataId to child components where needed, example-
UserCardComponent
<div [dataId]="'user-card'">
  <app-avatar [dataId]="'user-card-avatar'">
  <ion-text [dataId]="'user-card-details'">
</div>

Dynamic dataId Values:
[dataId]="componentVariable"
